verbose_text: The EGFLAM is located at chromosomal region 5p13.2-p13.1 (NCBI Gene, https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/gene) and is expressed in various tissues and organs including vascular smooth muscle (The Human Protein Atlas, http://www.protein-atlas.org).
